{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/ideas/tablet-as-keyboard","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>When you put a tablet into landscape orientation the keyboard has a very descent size for comfortable typing with two hands. But the rest of the screen is an area of a constant battle between the OS and an app leaving about one line for input preview.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; flex:1.3360655737704918;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/db02d86b94ebd568aa57f09dd6c2b6c0/e8496/tablet-keyboard.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.84662576687117%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Default keyboard\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/db02d86b94ebd568aa57f09dd6c2b6c0/6aca1/tablet-keyboard.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/db02d86b94ebd568aa57f09dd6c2b6c0/d2f63/tablet-keyboard.jpg 163w,\n/static/db02d86b94ebd568aa57f09dd6c2b6c0/c989d/tablet-keyboard.jpg 325w,\n/static/db02d86b94ebd568aa57f09dd6c2b6c0/6aca1/tablet-keyboard.jpg 650w,\n/static/db02d86b94ebd568aa57f09dd6c2b6c0/7c09c/tablet-keyboard.jpg 975w,\n/static/db02d86b94ebd568aa57f09dd6c2b6c0/01ab0/tablet-keyboard.jpg 1300w,\n/static/db02d86b94ebd568aa57f09dd6c2b6c0/e8496/tablet-keyboard.jpg 3761w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Not a long time ago I have started playing with vim, trying to work more efficiently without a mouse.</p>\n<p>But when my look stopped for a moment on a TV screen, I imagined that one can sit on a sofa, type on the tablet, and cast a picture from the tablet to the TV screen. If input will be on the TV screen only, then the tablet has some additional space to display hints, tips, and shortcuts (cheatsheet for vim, <a href=\"https://hamwaves.com/vim.tutorial/en/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">for example</a>).</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; flex:1.3360655737704918;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/fc6c3fbb2313828f4ede97afd0fb151f/d2602/tablet-keyboard-vim-cheatsheet.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.84662576687117%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Vim cheat sheet\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/fc6c3fbb2313828f4ede97afd0fb151f/6aca1/tablet-keyboard-vim-cheatsheet.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/fc6c3fbb2313828f4ede97afd0fb151f/d2f63/tablet-keyboard-vim-cheatsheet.jpg 163w,\n/static/fc6c3fbb2313828f4ede97afd0fb151f/c989d/tablet-keyboard-vim-cheatsheet.jpg 325w,\n/static/fc6c3fbb2313828f4ede97afd0fb151f/6aca1/tablet-keyboard-vim-cheatsheet.jpg 650w,\n/static/fc6c3fbb2313828f4ede97afd0fb151f/7c09c/tablet-keyboard-vim-cheatsheet.jpg 975w,\n/static/fc6c3fbb2313828f4ede97afd0fb151f/01ab0/tablet-keyboard-vim-cheatsheet.jpg 1300w,\n/static/fc6c3fbb2313828f4ede97afd0fb151f/d2602/tablet-keyboard-vim-cheatsheet.jpg 4032w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Instead of a TV screen, the keyboard app can be remotely connected to a regular PC. They can communicate using Bluetooth.</p>\n<p>Also to learn vim <a href=\"/ideas/agent-learns-vim-with-reinforcement-learning\">this reinforcement learning system</a> can help.</p>","excerpt":"When you put a tablet into landscape orientation the keyboard has a very descent size for comfortable typing with two hands. But the rest of…","tableOfContents":"","frontmatter":{"date":"May 16, 2020","published":"June 21, 2022","lastModified":"August 02, 2022","title":"Tablet as a keyboard","subtitle":null,"section":null,"draft":null,"developing":null,"buttonText":null,"buttonLink":null,"secondButtonText":null,"secondButtonLink":null,"featuredImage":{"publicURL":"/static/fc6c3fbb2313828f4ede97afd0fb151f/tablet-keyboard-vim-cheatsheet.jpg","childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fullWidth","backgroundColor":"#080808","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/fc6c3fbb2313828f4ede97afd0fb151f/e8061/tablet-keyboard-vim-cheatsheet.jpg","srcSet":"/static/fc6c3fbb2313828f4ede97afd0fb151f/cbfa3/tablet-keyboard-vim-cheatsheet.jpg 576w,\n/static/fc6c3fbb2313828f4ede97afd0fb151f/b3314/tablet-keyboard-vim-cheatsheet.jpg 768w,\n/static/fc6c3fbb2313828f4ede97afd0fb151f/e8061/tablet-keyboard-vim-cheatsheet.jpg 922w","sizes":"100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/fc6c3fbb2313828f4ede97afd0fb151f/4d1cf/tablet-keyboard-vim-cheatsheet.webp 576w,\n/static/fc6c3fbb2313828f4ede97afd0fb151f/7a6ea/tablet-keyboard-vim-cheatsheet.webp 768w,\n/static/fc6c3fbb2313828f4ede97afd0fb151f/ef6ad/tablet-keyboard-vim-cheatsheet.webp 922w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"100vw"}]},"width":1,"height":0.7505422993492408}}}}}},"pageContext":{"showLikes":true,"absolutePath":"/home/runner/work/mikolasan.github.io/mikolasan.github.i